What is the Nordea ID app?
The Nordea ID app is a means of identification you can download to your mobile device and use with your Nordea
access codes
. Your mobile device can either be a smartphone or a tablet. The app gives you secure access to Nordea’s banking services as well as other public online services.
When you have the Nordea ID app, you can log in to our online and mobile banking services, confirm online payments and access other public online services, such as Kela’s e-services and MyTax.
Benefits of the Nordea ID app:
You only need to choose and remember one 4–8 digit
PIN
.
You can
download the app on multiple devices
to ensure that you’ll always be able to access your banking services and other important services.
Requirements for using the app